Author: ddmar
Text: Nothing wrong with enjoying a burger. And 400 calories is too little food for anyone, especially someone who's anorexic and 5' 10''

Author: rolatbc123
Text: enjoy it! a burger is basically just a "standard" meal. eat it guilt free and then go back to try maintaining a happy medium between what youve been putting your body through (or whatever makes you feel best). :)
